reviewText: From 2005, but it still gave good coverage of their training that isn't shown anywhere else.
It helped a pal pass the test!

I want to be a special agent for the FBI I read almost every book available, so when I saw a dvd about how things go at quantico I snatched this dvd up. This dvd shows when a new class arrives and followed them through graduation. What they go through is really tough and challenging, after watching this dvd I now no what I need to do to get ready for this tough career.
